languages.text: {n}Издав булькающий звук, ксенос неторопливо, но неостановимо тянется к вашему глазу острым пальцем, практически прикасается к сетчатке... Но со вздохом останавливается.{/n} "Не сейчас. Может, позже".
{n}With a gurgling sound, the xenos slowly yet steadily moves his sharp finger to your eye, closer and closer, almost touching... then stops with a sigh.{/n} "Not now. Perhaps later."

traits.locale_text: {n}With a gurgling sound, the xenos casually yet unstoppably brings a sharp finger to your eye, closer and closer, almost touching it... then stops with a sigh.{/n} "Not now. There is always later."
traits.speaker: Haemonculae

languages.text: {n}Le xénos émet un gargouillis en pointant une griffe sur votre œil. Son doigt se rapproche inexorablement... Alors qu'il s'apprête à effleurer votre globe oculaire, il s'interrompt finalement dans un soupir.{/n} « Non, ce n'est pas le moment. Plus tard, peut-être. »
languages.original_text: {n}With a gurgling sound, the xenos slowly yet steadily moves his sharp finger to your eye, closer and closer, almost touching... then stops with a sigh.{/n} "Not now. Perhaps later."

traits.speaker: Haemonculae

languages.text: {n}这只异形喉咙发出了汩汩的声音，以缓慢而稳定的动作，将锋利的手指移向你的眼睛，越来越近，几乎要碰到你的眼球……随后，他叹了口气，停住了手。{/n}“现在还不行，以后再说吧。”

languages.text: {n}Mit einem gurgelnden Geräusch bewegt der Xenos langsam, aber stetig seinen spitzen Finger in Richtung deines Auges, näher und näher, berührt es fast ... und hält dann seufzend inne.{/n} "Nicht jetzt. Vielleicht später."

languages.text: {n}Con un sonido borboteante, el xenos mueve su afilado dedo lenta pero incesantemente hacia tu ojo, cada vez más cerca, hasta casi tocarlo... y luego se detiene soltando un suspiro.{/n} «Ahora no. Quizá después».

languages.text: {n}ゴリゴリと音を立てながら、異種族はゆっくりと、しかし着実に、その鋭い指をあなたの目に近づけて、触れそうになる…それから動きを止めため息をつく。{/n}「今はダメだ。また後で」

languages.text: {n}Keskin parmağını; ıslak bir ses eşliğinde, gözüne neredeyse dokunacak mesafeye gelene kadar, yavaşça ve dikkatle yaklaştırıyor. Sonrasında zeno, iç çekerek duruyor.{/n} "Şimdi değil. Belki sonra."
languages.original_text: {n}With a gurgling sound, the xenos slowly yet steadily moves his sharp finger to your eye, closer and closer, almost touching... then stops with a sigh.{/n} "Not now. Perhaps later."

traits.locale_text: {n}Zeno keskin parmağını, ıslak bir ses eşliğinde, gözüne neredeyse dokunacak mesafeye gelene kadar, yavaşça ve dikkatle yaklaştırıyor, ardından iç çekerek duruyor.{/n} "Şimdi değil. Belki sonra."
traits.speaker: Haemonculae
